subject: Baseball
lead_paragraph: PHOENIX, Aug. 22 (AP) — Brandon Webb allowed a run in the first inning, stopping his scoreless streak at 42 innings, but he won his sixth consecutive start to lead the Arizona Diamondbacks past the Milwaukee Brewers, 3-2, on Wednesday night.
